----------

Check it out on Steam ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/3615160/Teddys_Haven__A_Fantasy_Inspired_Shop_Simulator/

More about Teddy's Haven (from Steam):

An enchanted shop sim at the edge of a magical world.

Created In Loving Dedication To The Memory Of My Best Friend Teddy Bear.

Teddy’s Haven is a cozy fantasy shop simulator where you run a small, magical store nestled on the outskirts of a mysterious island. Specializing in potions, weapons, and enchanted curios, your humble haven draws in adventurers, wandering mages, and mystical creatures—each seeking something special beneath your warm, glowing lights.

Discover the Isle of Ursa

Your shop rests at the edge of Ursa, a magical island filled with ancient forests, glimmering lakes, and forgotten wonders. The land itself is imbued with quiet magic, responding to your care and growing alongside you as your shop flourishes.

As you nurture your haven, the island’s secrets begin to reveal themselves, with each change you make encouraging the land to unfold new mysteries. Your presence is felt here—this shop is not just a place of business, but a part of the very soul of Ursa.

Key Features:
Manage Your Dream Shop: Run your own cozy store, from stocking shelves to hiring magical employees and customizing every aspect of your shop's design.

Exploration & World Events: Venture into a rich, vibrant world full of surprises. Engage with dynamic seasonal and daily events that keep the world feeling alive and ever-changing.

Skill Systems: Unlock a variety of skills like stocking, harvesting, tending animals, and more.

New Game+: For those who want to restart and experience the game from a fresh perspective, the New Game+ system allows you to carry over your progress while experiencing the early changes in the world.

Ongoing Development: Teddy’s Haven is in Early Access, and your feedback will help shape the game’s future. With plans for new locations, minigames, world events, and more, the journey has only just begun.

snippet.title: Mid-East Crisis escalates - Iran rains missiles on Israel after attacks on nuclear sites | BBC News
snippet.description:
Iran has launched mass new strikes on Israel.  It says it attacked dozens of targets including military centres and airbases.   Smoke has been seen rising over the skyscrapers of Tel Aviv and there have been explosions in Jerusalem.  

The  bombardment is in retaliation for Israel's strikes on Iran, hitting military and nuclear sites.   It says it hit a nuclear facility in Isfahan following earlier strikes on the country's biggest nuclear facility at Natanz .Israel said the attacks were vital to prevent Iran developing a nuclear weapon.  

Iran’s spiritual leader, Ayatollah Khamenei, promised his country would 'inflict heavy blows' in response.
 
There are warnings the conflict could escalate into all-out war.  

Jane Hill presents BBC News at Ten reporting by Lucy Williamson, Ione Wells, Frank Gardner, Tom Bateman, Gary O’Donoghue and Lyse Doucet. 

Subscribe here: http://bit.ly/1rbfUog

For more news, analysis and features visit: www.bbc.com/news

snippet.description:
He's coming. Power Book IV: Force returns this fall on STARZ.

#PowerForce #PowerTV #PowerUniverse #PowerNeverEnds

Subscribe to the STARZ YouTube Channel for more Power: http://bit.ly/1kalhP0

Like Power Book IV: Force on Facebook: https://bit.ly/3wxEYO6
Follow Power Book IV: Force on Instagram: https://bit.ly/3c5eBpa

Facebook: http://starz.tv/STARZFacebookYT
Instagram: http://starz.tv/STARZInstagramYT
YouTube: https://starz.tv/STARZYouTube
TikTok: https://starz.tv/STARZTikTokYT

“Power Book IV: Force” centers on fan-favorite character Tommy Egan, played by Joseph Sikora, after he cuts ties and puts New York in his rearview mirror for good. As Tommy leaves New York after losing Ghost, LaKeisha and the only city he's ever known, he makes a quick detour to close an old wound that’s been haunting him for decades. What was supposed to be a quick stop turns into a labyrinth of family secrets and lies Tommy thought were long buried.  One step leads to another and Tommy quickly finds himself in Chicago's drug game, inserting himself between the city's two biggest crews. In a city divided by race, Tommy straddles the line, ultimately becoming the lynchpin that not only unites them - but holds the POWER to watch them crumble. As the first season unfolds at breakneck speed, Tommy uses his outsider status to his advantage, breaking all the local rules and rewriting them on his quest to become the biggest drug dealer in Chicago.
